{"tid":2254331,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"人生苦短，又係時候行山","createTime":"2020-10-22T17:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T17:49:38.000Z","uid":158199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e05e89eeb53ca619aa35b551aba6bf85c722e944","tid":2254331,"uid":158199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人生苦短，又係時候行山，日日困住係屋企防疫愈困愈攰?<br />\n咁就啱，不如出來行下山，總要過番正常的生活吧，順便出來行下當做下運動。<br />\n最近去咗浪茄，一個非常美麗的地方，留在香港，走入郊野，暫時忘記手頭上的工作，行一個山仔輕鬆一下吧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/MPtX31d/01272421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FMPtX31d%2F01272421.jpg&h=3af34a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/ssFj47b/01272390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FssFj47b%2F01272390.jpg&h=22b97046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣的朋友可以填以下Google Form，我們見到會盡快加你入去<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScA-eMPnlmnNe40A2ZhvQcMsdHXxkK8if_5y7su0B7Q8Jakxg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScA-eMPnlmnNe40A2ZhvQcMsdHXxkK8if_5y7su0B7Q8Jakxg%2Fviewform&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=6f3625ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScA-eMPnlmnNe40A2ZhvQcMsdHXxkK8if_5y7su0B7Q8Jakxg/viewform</a></blockquote>"}]}